===Greece===
'''[[Hellenic Parliament]]''':

According to the [[Constitution of Greece]] each law is approved by the [[Hellenic Parliament|parliament]] and promulgated by the [[President of Greece|President of the Republic]].

{{quote|"We, the President of the Hellenic Republic, do promulgate the following law approved by the parliament:..."}}
